ğŸ©º Diabetes Readmission Prediction

This project explores the **US Diabetes Readmission dataset (~100k encounters, ~70k patients)** to analyze hospital readmission patterns and build a predictive model. It covers the full data science workflow: **data preparation, exploratory analysis, modeling, deployment, SQL insights, and dashboarding**.

